    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Proposed Solutions\"\nsubtitle: \"Closing the 51.3% unrecognized gap — a prioritised roadmap\"\n---\n\n\n\n## The Unrecognized Population\n\n::: {#40458872 .cell execution_count=2}\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div>            <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.5/MathJax.js?config=TeX-AMS-MML_SVG\"></script><script>if (window.MathJax && window.MathJax.Hub && window.MathJax.Hub.Config) {window.MathJax.Hub.Config({SVG: {font: \"STIX-Web\"}});}</script>                <script>window.PlotlyConfig = {MathJaxConfig: 'local'};</script>\n        <script charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-3.5.0.min.js\" integrity=\"sha256-fHbNLP+GlIXN+efbQec78UkemUz3NJp7UmfGxC1tNxs=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>                <div id=\"b0ea9a3e-b422-4320-b293-e67eabe7d793\" class=\"plotly-graph-div\" style=\"height:380px; width:100%;\"></div>            <script>                window.PLOTLYENV=window.PLOTLYENV || {};                                if (document.getElementById(\"b0ea9a3e-b422-4320-b293-e67eabe7d793\")) {                    Plotly.newPlot(                        \"b0ea9a3e-b422-4320-b293-e67eabe7d793\",                        [{\"hole\":0.5,\"hovertemplate\":\"\\u003cb\\u003e%{label}\\u003c\\u002fb\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e%{value:,} rows\\u003cbr\\u003e%{percent}\\u003cextra\\u003e\\u003c\\u002fextra\\u003e\",\"insidetextorientation\":\"radial\",\"labels\":[\"No\\u002fZero Purchase History\",\"Very Low History (1\\u20134 units)\",\"Price Out of DBSCAN Range\"],\"marker\":{\"colors\":[\"#ef4444\",\"#f97316\",\"#f59e0b\"],\"line\":{\"color\":\"white\",\"width\":3}},\"textfont\":{\"family\":\"Inter, sans-serif\",\"size\":11},\"textinfo\":\"label+percent\",\"values\":[47,31400,21900],\"type\":\"pie\"}],                        {\"template\":{\"data\":{\"histogram2dcontour\":[{\"type\":\"histogram2dcontour\",\"colorbar\":{\"outlinewidth\":0,\"ticks\":\"\"},\"colorscale\":[[0