te citation quality and build the analyst review workflow. Requires prompt engineering, de-duplication, and a write-back feedback loop before scaling.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n| Solution | Reach | Effort | Analyst Input Needed |\n|:---------|------:|:------:|:--------------------:|\n| B — Similar-product transfer | ~31\\,400 rows | Medium | Yes — criteria definition |\n| A — Agentic search | ~47 rows | High | Yes — citation sign-off |\n\n",
